---
title: Cal Smart Harissa-Spiced Turkey with Almond Pilaf
description: You won't believe a meal this good is also calorie-conscious! A seasoned rice pilaf is accented with toasted almonds for some nutty crunch, while North African-spiced turkey and veggies bring warm, earthy vibes to complete the dish!

